content:
Channel Rules:
1. 🤝 Keep it Friendly
  - Respect other members
  - No harassment or hate speech
  - Be patient with beginners
2. 💻 Stay On Topic
  - Keep discussions code and development focused
  - Use appropriate channels for different topics
  - Save casual chat for #general
3. 📝 Share Code Properly
  - Use code blocks for sharing code snippets
  - Include relevant error messages
  - Provide context when asking for help
4. 🌟 Be Constructive
  - Offer solutions, not criticism
  - Acknowledge helpful responses
  - Share knowledge to help others learn
